{"tid":1882221,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[社畜文化] 1天增12確診　1個飯局10人中招 範圍擴　日現多宗不明感染","createTime":"2020-02-16T06:10:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T10:18:22.000Z","uid":51620,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"35ac5f800783b3bd04d331819f0f8f2e918f38f8","tid":1882221,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T06:10:50.000Z","msg":"日本武漢肺炎疫情擴大，撇除「鑽石公主號」郵輪個案，昨共新增12宗確診個案，其中東京都八宗、和歌山縣三宗、愛知縣一宗。鑑於感染人數持續增加，多個新增病例感染途徑不明，政府成立專家小組跟進可能出現的社區傳播。<br />\n<br />\n東京都新增的八宗病例中，七宗與2月13日確診的70多歲的士司機有關，同樣參加個人的士工會分部在東京都屋形船舉辦的新年會。七人中有四人是50多歲到80多歲的男性的士司機，另有兩人是跟其中兩名司機同住的50多歲到60多歲女性，剩下一人則是在屋形船上工作的40多歲男性；該飯局至今共10人確診。該名的士司機住在神奈川縣的80歲岳母亦確診感染，在女婿確診當日死亡，是日本首宗武漢肺炎死亡案例。餘下一名患者是40多歲上班族。東京都累計有11宗確診病例。<br />\n<br />\n至於和歌山濟生會有田醫院就疑爆發院內感染，繼一名50多歲醫生和一名曾短暫住院的70多歲男子日前確診後，昨再有一名50多歲醫生、他的妻子，以及一名病人確診。由於早前確診的醫生與前日確診的患者並無接觸，和歌山縣知事仁坂吉伸曾表示並非院內感染，然而院內再有醫生確診，和歌山縣政府正查明傳染途徑。該縣現有共五宗確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n愛知縣名古屋昨亦新增一宗確診個案，患者是一名60多歲女子，他是前日確診男子的妻子，兩人曾一同去美國夏威夷旅行。撇除「鑽石公主號」郵輪的確診個案，日本全國共有53宗確診個案，當中一人死亡，北至北海道、南至沖繩縣都有確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n泰國新增一宗個案，患者是曾經接觸確診患者的醫護人員，是當地首宗醫護人員感染個案。當地累計有34宗確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/FsNACQvLj7irc-p0mSuhhzMRzxc=/802x560/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/NEIWX43AMC4KEG6JHXN35CMP4I.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FFsNACQvLj7irc-p0mSuhhzMRzxc%3D%2F802x560%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FNEIWX43AMC4KEG6JHXN35CMP4I.gif&h=c51624b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200216/7GDRXNWKBQTWF4HNJJUQ72D2HA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR27TM8loWL9hc3g4h7a20SD7oIq5NzgVeIIAT-zqma3_YOpykWeVFsJynY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200216%2F7GDRXNWKBQTWF4HNJJUQ72D2HA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR27TM8loWL9hc3g4h7a20SD7oIq5NzgVeIIAT-zqma3_YOpykWeVFsJynY&d=sh6QB3P1ZXxG4EHsBexfbgoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=1fde747b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200216%2F7GDRXNWKBQTWF4HNJJUQ72D2HA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR27TM8loWL9hc3g4h7a20SD7oIq5NzgVeIIAT-zqma3_YOpykWeVFsJynY&h=ef105a7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200216/7GDRXNWKBQTWF4HNJJUQ72D2HA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR27TM8loWL9hc3g4h7a20SD7oIq5NzgVeIIAT-zqma3_YOpykWeVFsJynY</a>"},{"pid":"54202ee786da43f58d5ffe1efa812f381b7e39be","tid":1882221,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T06:12:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">該名的士司機住在神奈川縣的80歲岳母亦確診感染，在女婿確診當日死亡</span></span><br />\n屌，絕對心理陰影"},{"pid":"f77503153b9a9d8e15702670b5950dc00c300b21","tid":1882221,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54202ee786da43f58d5ffe1efa812f381b7e39be","tid":1882221,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T06:12:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">該名的士司機住在神奈川縣的80歲岳母亦確診感染，在女婿確診當日死亡</span></span><br />\n屌，絕對心理陰影"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T06:16:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44125c0b2d9167b5e54dc0ecb34710c62dd11efc","tid":1882221,"uid":106348,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"